description.narrative: The project development objective (PDO) is to increase the productivity, profitability, and market access of the farming community in Maharashtra. This would be achieved by strengthening farmers' capacity through technical knowledge, market intelligence, and market networks to support diversification and intensification of agriculture production aimed at responding to market demand. Farmers will also be assisted through farmer organizations, alternative market channels developed outside of regulated markets, and improved services provided by modernizing the promising traditional wholesale markets.
